                    <span>The review from "A reader" is erroneous. There is no review from "Leon Brooks," so it is unlikely there is any business relationship with a non-existent person.<P>I imagine "A reader" meant Leon *Starr* who runs an entirely separate business from those run by either of the authors. Sure, we talk and refer business each other's way, but that is to be expected. Please delete "A reader"'s review.<P>(If you know Leon, you'd know he says what he really thinks, even if--especially?--it's bad!)</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Shame!</div>
